                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For the text of the Communiqué of the First Quebec Conference which Roosevelt
                    read during this press conference, see <hi rend="italic">post</hi>, <ref
                        target="#pg_1157">p. 1157</ref>. For the informal remarks which Mackenzie
                    King, Churchill, and Roosevelt made to the press, see Rosenman, pp. 355–365.</p>
